    • BreakerFalconDiffDrive

      public BreakerFalconDiffDrive​(com.ctre.phoenix.motorcontrol.can.WPI_TalonFX[] leftMotors, com.ctre.phoenix.motorcontrol.can.WPI_TalonFX[] rightMotors, boolean invertL, boolean invertR, BreakerGenericGyro imu, BreakerDiffDriveConfig driveConfig)
      Creates a new Differential (tank drive) drivetrain instance.
      Parameters:
      leftMotors - Left WPI_TalonFX motors.
      invertL - Invert left motor outputs & encoder readings.
      rightMotors - Right WPI_TalonFX motors.
      invertR - Invert right motor outputs & encoder readings.
      gyro - BreakerGenericGyro capable of reading yaw.
      driveConfig - A BreakerDiffDriveConfig representing the configerable values of this drivetrain's kinimatics and control values
